name: LacOx120
description: pFX92 with 120 tandem copies of the lacO operator site separated by 10 random bp, cloned using the NheI and XbaI sites. pFX92 is a derivative of pUC18 with the following MCS (-EcoRI-BamHI-XhoI-NheI-SmaI-XbaI-SalI-BglII-HindIII-).

name: TetOx120-Kan-TetOx120
description: pFX92 with two cassettes of 120 tandem copies of the tetO operator separated by a kan gene. The insert was cloned using the NheI and XbaI sites. pFX92 is a derivative of pUC18 with the following MCS (-EcoRI-BamHI-XhoI-NheI-SmaI-XbaI-SalI-BglII-HindIII-).

name: pCSN
notes: From Uffe Mortensen. Integration vector for use with CASCADE copy number amplification strains (e.g. R1706) Vector requires USER cloning. Prepare vector via overnight AsiSI digest followed by Nb.bsmI digest. Treat PCR product with USER enzyme mix (NEB)
